description: With a FM Transmitter, you can transmit your favorite tunes from portable music players to your car stereo quickly and easily. Just plug the FM transmitter into your portable devices and the adaptor into the car cigar lighter. Tune your car stereo or receiver to the clearest FM frequency, and enjoy your digital music with full sound and convenience.
title: Excelvan FM Transmitter Car Charger Adapter For BlackBerry /Sony / Samsung and mp3/mp4 Player
